            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Other details include a unique BOVET 1822 clock created just for the client. There’s also a Montblac pen stored in a hand-crafted aluminum and leather case inside the glovebox. Guilloche instrument panel dials are finished like some of the finest jewelry or watches in the world.",
